          </mj-text>
          <mj-text>
            And one airline at least managed to soar gracefully into the post-COVID skies. Read how easyJet leveraged RICOH Spaces to support flexible hybrid working—enabling a safe return to work, facilitating greater employee collaboration, and more cost-effective use of space.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text>
            RICOH Spaces is your platform to design and manage a workplace that keeps up with how your teams meet up, socialise, and collaborate.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text>
            It is all about:
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>

      <mj-section padding="0">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-table cellpadding="10px" cellspacing="5px">
            <tr>
              <td style="line-height: 1;"><img style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" width="30" height="30" src="https://ricoh-email.2xcode.dev/images/edm-hw/check-mark-button.png" alt="" /></td>
              <td style="padding-left: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Providing a seamless employee and customer experience</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="line-height: 1;"><img style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" width="30" height="30" src="https://ricoh-email.2xcode.dev/images/edm-hw/check-mark-button.png" alt="" /></td>
              <td style="padding-left: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Bringing workplace analytics and management under one roof</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="line-height: 1;"><img style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" width="30" height="30" src="https://ricoh-email.2xcode.dev/images/edm-hw/check-mark-button.png" alt="" /></td>
              <td style="padding-left: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Combining the best of on-site and remote working</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="line-height: 1;"><img style="width: 30px; height: 30px;" width="30" height="30" src="https://ricoh-email.2xcode.dev/images/edm-hw/check-mark-button.png" alt="" /></td>
              <td style="padding-left: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Maximising return on investment, ensuring data security, and minimising risks</td>
            </tr>
          </mj-table>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>

      <mj-section>
        <mj-column width="90%" background-color="#f3f3f3" padding="20px">
